(113, 'Giày Gucci Unisex Ace GG Supreme Sneaker With Bees', 'giay-gucci-unisex-ace-gg-supreme-sneaker-with-bees', 'uploads/product/1594472897_giay-gucci-women-s-ace-gg-supreme-sneaker-with-bees-5e057d119f154-27122019104001.jpg', 23, 14100000, 13900000, 1, 1, 1, 0, 16, 'gucci.com', 'h018989', 9, 2, 'Kiểu dáng: Sneakers\r\nGiới tính: Unisex\r\nMàu sắc: Xanh phối đỏ', '<p><a href=\"https://vuahanghieu.com/gucci/giay\">Gi&agrave;y Gucci</a>&nbsp;Unisex Ace GG Supreme Sneaker With Bees - Thiết kế hiện đại với phong c&aacute;ch trẻ trung, năng động. Với t&ocirc;ng m&agrave;u xanh, đỏ nổi bật l&agrave;m điểm nhấn.<br />\r\nGi&agrave;y được l&agrave;m từ chất liệu Da + vải cao cấp bền đẹp, thời gian sử dụng l&acirc;u d&agrave;i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"500\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/giay-gucci-women-s-ace-gg-supreme-sneaker-with-bees-5e057d119f8c9-27122019104001.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>TH&Ocirc;NG TIN CHUNG</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>KIỂU D&Aacute;NG: Sneakers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>GIỚI T&Iacute;NH: Unisex</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>M&Agrave;U SẮC: Xanh phối đỏ</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>CHẤT LIỆU: Da + Vải cao cấp</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>PHONG C&Aacute;CH: Hiện đại, năng động, trẻ trung</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>XUẤT XỨ: &Yacute;</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, '2020-07-11 06:08:17', '2020-07-11 06:08:17'),
(114, 'Giày Sneaker Gucci Ace Kingsnake Print Màu Đen', 'giay-sneaker-gucci-ace-kingsnake-print-mau-den', 'uploads/product/1594473356_giay-sneaker-gucci-ace-kingsnake-print-mau-den-5eeb2a250ac2d-18062020154733.jpg', 20, 13500000, 12900000, 1, 1, 1, 0, 16, 'gucci.com', 'h024150', 9, 2, 'Kiểu dáng: Sneakers\r\nGiới tính: Unisex\r\nMàu sắc: Đen', '<p><strong>Gi&agrave;y Sneaker Gucci Ace Kingsnake Print M&agrave;u Đen</strong>&nbsp;- thiết kế hiện đại, trẻ trung đến từ thương hiệu Gucci nổi tiếng. Với đ&ocirc;i gi&agrave;y sneaker thời trang n&agrave;y chắc chắn sẽ gi&uacute;p bạn trở n&ecirc;n nổi bật v&agrave; cuốn h&uacute;t hơn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Phần tr&ecirc;n bề mặt của gi&agrave;y l&agrave;m bằng chất liệu da cao cấp, ph&iacute;a sau được may th&ecirc;m miếng da xanh l&aacute; v&agrave; đỏ l&agrave;m nổi bật đ&ocirc;i gi&agrave;y. Xung quanh gi&agrave;y được may với c&aacute;c đường chỉ kh&acirc;u cực k&igrave; chắc chắn v&agrave; tỉ mỉ đảm bảo h&agrave;i l&ograve;ng ngay với cả kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng kh&oacute; t&iacute;nh nhất.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"500\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/giay-sneaker-gucci-ace-kingsnake-print-mau-den-5eeb2a2551ab2-18062020154733.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"500\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/giay-sneaker-gucci-ace-kingsnake-print-mau-den-5eeb2a245ead9-18062020154732.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '2020-07-11 06:15:56', '2020-07-11 06:15:56'),
(115, 'Nike Renew Run', 'nike-renew-run', 'uploads/product/1594473856_renew-run-running-shoe-bCz58M (2).jpg', 20, 2600000, 2490000, 1, 1, 1, 0, 16, 'nike.vn', 'NK321', 8, 6, 'Chưa có tóm tắt', '<p>The Nike Renew Run keeps you moving with softer foam for a cushioned feel. Designed with the everyday runner in mind, this shoe delivers secure support and durable traction for comfort on the go.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"625\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/renew-run-running-shoe-bCz58M.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"625\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/renew-run-running-shoe-bCz58M%20(3).jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '2020-07-11 06:24:16', '2020-07-11 06:24:16'),
(116, 'Nike Aqua Rift', 'nike-aqua-rift', 'uploads/product/1594474076_aqua-rift-shoe-C3VX3v (2).jpg', 20, 3700000, 3500000, 1, 1, 1, 0, 16, 'nike.vn', 'NK833', 8, 2, 'Chưa có tóm tắt', '<p>Blending features from 2 classic &#39;90s style influences, the Nike Aqua Rift takes retro beach style into the present with a futuristic silhouette and an exaggerated stance. Featuring the iconic split toe from Nike Air Rift, it looks like nothing else on the streets. Larger-than-life shapes and cartoonish colours from the Nike Aqua line put the upper in a time and place all of its own.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"625\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/aqua-rift-shoe-C3VX3v.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"625\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/aqua-rift-shoe-C3VX3v%20(1).jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '2020-07-11 06:27:56', '2020-07-11 06:27:56'),
(117, 'Nike Air Force 1 Shadow', 'nike-air-force-1-shadow', 'uploads/product/1594475785_air-force-1-shadow-shoe-mN8Glx (5).jpg', 20, 3500000, 3230000, 1, 1, 1, 0, 16, 'nike.vn', 'NK421', 8, 2, 'Chưa có tóm tắt', '<p>The Nike Air Force 1 Shadow puts a playful twist on the classic b-ball design. Using a layered approach, doubling the branding and exaggerating the midsole, it highlights AF-1 DNA with a bold, feminine look.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"625\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/air-force-1-shadow-shoe-mN8Glx%20(4).jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"625\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/air-force-1-shadow-shoe-mN8Glx.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"625\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/aqua-rift-shoe-C3VX3v%20(1)(1).jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '2020-07-11 06:56:25', '2020-07-11 06:56:25'),
(118, 'Nike Renew Run', 'nike-renew-run', 'uploads/product/1594476244_renew-run-running-shoe-bCz58M (4).jpg', 25, 2700000, 2499000, 1, 1, 1, 0, 16, 'nike.vn', 'NK973', 8, 2, 'Chưa có tóm tắt', '<p>The Nike Renew Run keeps you moving with softer foam for a cushioned feel. Designed with the everyday runner in mind, this shoe delivers secure support and durable traction for comfort on the go.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"625\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/renew-run-running-shoe-bCz58M%20(7).jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"625\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/renew-run-running-shoe-bCz58M%20(5).jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '2020-07-11 07:04:04', '2020-07-11 07:04:04'),
(119, 'Nike React Infinity Run Flyknit', 'nike-react-infinity-run-flyknit', 'uploads/product/1594476489_react-infinity-run-flyknit-running-shoe-xC1vr3.jpg', 18, 4699000, 3699000, 1, 1, 1, 0, 16, 'nike.vn', 'NK986', 8, 5, 'Chưa có tóm tắt', '<p>The Nike React Infinity Run Flyknit is designed to keep you on the run. More foam and improved upper details provide a secure and cushioned feel. Lace up and feel the potential as you hit the road.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"625\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/react-infinity-run-flyknit-running-shoe-xC1vr3%20(3).jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"625\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/react-infinity-run-flyknit-running-shoe-xC1vr3%20(5).jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"625\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/react-infinity-run-flyknit-running-shoe-xC1vr3%20(6).jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '2020-07-11 07:08:09', '2020-07-14 09:03:06'),
(120, 'Jordan Jumpman', 'jordan-jumpman', 'uploads/product/1594476720_jordan-jumpman-wristbands-D8PVKz.jpg', 19, 259000, 229000, 1, 1, 1, 0, 17, 'nike.vn', 'NK097', 8, 2, 'Chưa có tóm tắt', '<p>Channel the spirit of one of the greats in the Jordan Jumpman Wristbands. Made from stretchy material for a secure fit, they feature sweat-wicking technology to help keep you dry, comfortable and focused whether you&#39;re on or off the court.</p>', NULL, NULL, '2020-07-11 07:12:00', '2020-07-14 07:53:23'),
(121, 'Jordan Flight', 'jordan-flight', 'uploads/product/1594476903_jordan-flight-crew-basketball-socks-ZJ9557.jpg', 18, 459000, 429000, 1, 1, 1, 0, 17, 'nike.vn', 'NK056', 8, 2, 'Chưa có tóm tắt', '<p>The Jordan Flight Crew Basketball Socks feature a plush design with targeted cushioning to help keep you comfortable on the court. Mesh ventilation zones and sweat-wicking technology help keep you cool and dry through the 4th quarter.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"625\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/jordan-flight-crew-basketball-socks-ZJ9557%20(1).jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '2020-07-11 07:15:03', '2020-07-14 08:46:48'),
(122, 'Nike Air SNEAKR Sox', 'nike-air-sneakr-sox', 'uploads/product/1594477032_air-sneakr-sox-crew-socks-DZkk9W.jpg', 20, 459000, 429000, 1, 1, 1, 0, 17, 'nike.vn', 'NK437', 8, 2, 'Chưa có tóm tắt', '<p>The Nike Air SNEAKR Sox feature premium fabric combined with cushioning at the toe and heel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"625\" src=\"/ckfinder/userfiles/images/Product/air-sneakr-sox-crew-socks-DZkk9W.jpg\" width=\"500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '2020-07-11 07:17:12', '2020-07-11 07:17:12');

